    <div class="main review-item" id="1335689">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1335689/" class="title-link">唯一一本简明的中文逻辑读物，而且还写的很正确</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1335689"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/franco/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/franco/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Franco</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-03-25"
      class="main-meta">2008-03-25 22:29:25</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1335689_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  由于众所周知的原因，中文的逻辑读物往往采用黑格尔的“正反合”理论。造成的结果则是教授逻辑的读物多为繁复，读之如催眠。  此书应写于抗战时期（书中有大学生领救济金之事）。采取的是对话体，因此读来犹如小说。悬念重重，令人颇为心折，欲读之而后快。  本书却说理清晰，...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1335689/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">7有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
